abstract: Occupy Wall Street organizers have announced plans to hold a gathering at Chase Manhattan Plaza in Lower Manhattan to commemorate the start of the movement, but the site has been fenced off since September, Colin Moynihan reports in The New York Times.

headline.main: Suit Seeks Plans for JPMorgan's Fenced-Off Plaza
